channel.title: My sever wont go back online?
channel.description:
Hi I recently had my server online,
Suddenly the next day I could not connect through my server's ip anymore.
I tried to re-register at moparscape server status and it told me that my server was offline!
I had not changed any settings at all!
Yes I had it clearly running and other players on the night before! Why has this happened, also how do I fix this?
Note: I have reset my settings for my router and no-ip
Still will not go on!
Please Help!
